      • offlineRoutingTilesPath

        public abstract NavigationViewOptions.Builder offlineRoutingTilesPath(String offlinePath)
        Add an offline path for loading offline routing data.

        When added, the NavigationView will try to initialize and use this data for offline routing when no or poor internet connection is found.

        Parameters:
        offlinePath - to offline data on device
        Returns:
        this builder

      • offlineRoutingTilesVersion

        public abstract NavigationViewOptions.Builder offlineRoutingTilesVersion(String offlineVersion)
        Add an offline tile version. When providing a routing tile path, this version is also required for configuration.

        This version should directly correspond to the data in the offline path also provided.

        Parameters:
        offlineVersion - of data in tile path
        Returns:
        this builder
